data.description:
Welcome to an exceptional townhouse in the coveted Kipling Klub complex! This property is a rare find, offering easy access to both public transportation and main highways for convenient commuting.

This 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom townhouse comes with a coveted 2-car attached garage—a real bonus. The open and expansive living room floor plan fills the space with natural light, creating a warm and welcoming atmosphere. The freshly cleaned carpet flooring and freshly painted walls adds to the overall appeal.

The master bedroom and master bathroom on the main level provide a convenient and comfortable living space. The galley kitchen, with its cozy charm and laminate counters, opens up to an outdoor deck—an ideal spot to unwind.

Upstairs, you'll find two nicely sized bedrooms and a full bathroom, ensuring flexibility for various living arrangements. The basement is not just for storage; it houses a cozy den, a laundry area with hookups, and provides easy access to the attached garage.

The location is truly great, offering instant access to shopping, parks, walking trails, lakes, and a convenient drive to both the mountains and the city. This property is indeed amazing, and you wouldn't want to miss out on it!
